   "Aircraft (ER-2) Laser Infrared Absorption Spectrometer (ALIAS) for
   In-situ Stratospheric Measurements of HCl, N[2]O, CH[4], NO[2], and
   HNO[3]", C.R. Webster, R.D. May, C.A. Trimble, R.G. Chave and J.
   Kendall, Applied Optics, 33, 454-472, 1994.

   "Evolution of HCl Concentrations in the L. Stratosphere from 1991 to
   1996 Following the Eruption of Mt. Pinatubo", CR Webster, RD May, HA
   Michelsen, DC Scott, JC Wilson, HH Jonsson, CA Brock, JE Dye, D
   Baumgardner, RM Stimpfle, JP Koplow, JJ Margitan, MH Proffitt, L
   Jaegle, RL Herman, H Hu, GJ Flesch, and M Loewenstein, Geophys. Res.
   Lett., 25, 995-998, 1998.

   "Measurements of CO in the upper troposphere and lower stratosphere",
   RL Herman, CR Webster, RD May, DC Scott, H Hu, EJ Moyer, PO Wennberg,
   TF Hanisco, EJ Lanzendorf, RJ Salawitch, YL Yung, JJ Margitan, TP Bui,
   Chemosphere: Global Change Science, 1, 173-183, 1999.

